EA needs to change many things in their next tournaments! 
They should make restrictions like:
-  Max Icons per team set to two (Like the Olympic Games) 
- max 90+ overrall players set to three 
- Games should also be played with normal squads, not only FUT 
- Emphasize on giving viewers tips on tactics / instructions / formations and others ( Most of the time they don't show formation screen or discuss anything apart from dribiling) 
- Work with picks and bans 
- Each player picks a team that can be banned or picked 
- Managers are useless in FUT this is wrong 
- Each player should get a transfer card that allows you to transfer your favorite player to another league you admire! (Example: I like David Villa, but He plays at MLS and is Spanish, I can`t use him at Calcio unless I have spanish or icons, so Every player should get for experience points or freely a card that allows up to 1 Favorite player transfer to any league you desire!) 

Conclusion: 
Games are really boring, players play basiclly the same, have the same players, most of them aren`t affordable, gameplay is very mainstream and monotonus, they don`t look at all as a football match!!! EA needs to keep the game real and make silver and gold players more commun, it would be much better and exciting to watch! Please Consider this We love FIFA but you need to make it worth watching... Only De Gea and Yashin used? this is boring!!!!! Needs to have changes!!!
